  "detailed_description": "Reactivated is a first-person horror game in dark sci-fi settings.<br />\r\nPlayers are to explore, survive and make decisions that will affect the outcome at the end, which are 2 at the moment.<br />\r\nThere are no intended jump-scares, only the chill on your back when you get to the point where you'll realize: “There are no jump-scares.”<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n“For we do not have a high priest who is unable to empathize with our weaknesses, but we have one who has been tempted in every way, just as we are—yet he did not sin.”<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHebrews 4:15",
